:{{DIcon}} How have things been?
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 501026907: Config/Level/Mission/5010269/Act/Act501026907.json-->
::'''Molly:''' Ugh, how do you think I've been? I've just been so angry with my coworkers...
::'''Molly:''' I just feel like... I've grown numb to it already. There's really no reason for me to put up with the military. Whatever nonsense they get up to has no bearing on my life. So why should I be making myself miserable?
::'''Molly:''' ...Is this really the life that I want? Back then, I did everything I could to get into the Technology Division, but I didn't do all that just so I could lie back and wait for my life to be over.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You are doing the right thing. Keep at it.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501026967-->
:::'''Molly:''' Easier said than done.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I don't think you need to put yourself through all that either.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501026969-->
:::'''Molly:''' You're right, but I don't dare to imagine how things would change if I give up everything. Am I really going to stand here and watch Belobog get worse by the day?
:::'''Molly:''' To be honest, I'm scared. It's not just because the environment is getting worse. What's even more terrifying is that I will end up just like those people. I'll become the worst version of myself.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Whatever you're passionate about is what your life really is...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501026972-->
:::'''Molly:''' So you're saying... I should do what I truly love?
:::'''Molly:''' But after all the upsetting things I've experienced... I feel as if I'll never find something that I can completely throw myself into.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_501026974-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501026974-->
::'''Molly:''' I don't know how long I'll be able to hold on... but I will try to stick with it a little longer. It was nice chatting with you. Thanks.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_501026907-->
:{{DIcon|Exit}} Have a nice day. Bye.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
